law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 226, sec. 113, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 57, sec. 4, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 114, sec. 10. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 58, sec. 17, effective March 5, 1952.
